{"word":"G1913 - ἐπιβιβάζω - epibibázō - ep-ee-bee-bad'-zo - Set on","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιβιβάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epibibázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-bee-bad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Set on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஏற்று"},{"paragraph":"to cause to mount; to place upon"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a reduplicated derivation of the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G307 - ἀναβιβάζω - anabibázō - an-ab-ee-bad'-zo/307\">G307</a>); to <i>cause to mount</i> (an animal): - set on.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}